{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"1654355696d4537416":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"165435569617ad798b-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Welcome to Swiss-Belresort Pecatu!","heading_size":"h1"}},"165435569617ad798b-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Swiss-Belresort Pecatu is a four-star international resort in the hilly resort complex known as Pecatu Indah Resort. Located on the southern peninsula of Bali, a popular area for surfers, golfers, honeymooners and those who are travelling to Bali looking for serenity.<\/p>"}},"165435569617ad798b-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["165435569617ad798b-0","165435569617ad798b-1","165435569617ad798b-2"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"background-1","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":16}},"16544821004b982cac":{"type":"video","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"h1","cover_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_9356.jpg","video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yDonkL_lNiw","description":"","full_width":false,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"1654740138e6563a66":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"16547401387b5facea-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"h1"}},"16547401387b5facea-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Hotel Address<\/strong><\/p><p>Indah Resort Bali, <br\/>Pecatu Indah Raya Blok G2, Pecatu, <br\/>Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, <br\/>Bali 80361, Indonesia. <\/p><p>16 minutes drive from the airport<\/p><p><br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["16547401387b5facea-0","16547401387b5facea-1"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"background-1","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":20}},"1654493355c458ff05":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"1654493355120a8204-0":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"CHSE Certification","text":"<p>Swiss-Belresort Pecatu has been certified for the Cleanliness, Health, Safety and Environmental sustainability (CHSE) Standards set<br\/>by the Ministry of Tourism and Creative Economy \/ Tourism and<br\/>Creative Economy of the Republic of Indonesia.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"1654493355120a8204-1":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"Accessibility","text":"<p>Located at a prime resort complex, Swiss-Belresort Pecatu is just a stone's throw away from Dreamland beach and other tourist destinations. More than this, the hotel is also committed to making sure that the resort is accessible to all. Hence, the management have made sure that the property is wheel-chair accessible. <\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"1654493355120a8204-2":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"Covid-19 Safety","text":"<p>Hotel check-in\/out is completely contactless and cashless transactions are available for all charges at the property. Hotel rooms are also sealed and left vacant for 72 hours between stays. Masks, temperature checks, sanitizers, and individually-wrapped food options are also available.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["1654493355120a8204-0","1654493355120a8204-1","1654493355120a8204-2"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":"h1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","columns_desktop":3,"column_alignment":"left","background_style":"primary","button_label":"","button_link":"","color_scheme":"background-1","columns_mobile":"1","swipe_on_mobile":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":36}},"16544987438768b0f3":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"16544987431e07e2a4-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Property Highlights","heading_size":"h1"}},"16544987431e07e2a4-1":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p>Share information about your brand with your customers. Describe a product, make announcements, or welcome customers to your store.<\/p>"}},"16544987431e07e2a4-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["16544987431e07e2a4-0","16544987431e07e2a4-1","16544987431e07e2a4-2"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"background-1","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0}},"16544858666e8305a3":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"165448586626332252-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Expansive Guestrooms","heading_size":"h2"}},"165448586626332252-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The resort boasts 199 spacious bedrooms fully equipped with air-conditioning, minibar, refrigerator, in-room safe, LED television, and fast WiFi.<\/p><p><br\/>Participants will be in either double or triple sharing rooms. <\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"165448586626332252-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["165448586626332252-0","165448586626332252-1","165448586626332252-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/KING_-_DELUXE_BALCONY.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"1654501931b2357ccb":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"165450193108e0638e-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Splendid Amenities","heading_size":"h2"}},"165450193108e0638e-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The resort features facilities designed to make the most of a guest's stay. These include a lagoon swimming pool, fitness center, business center, and valet parking.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"165450193108e0638e-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["165450193108e0638e-0","165450193108e0638e-1","165450193108e0638e-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_9391.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_fi